OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny morning cloud clearing to
OL,6,Fleave another dry and sunny day. The
OL,7,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Remaining hot, though a
OL,9,Flittle cooler towards the northwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMost seeing clear spells
OL,12,Fovernight with intermittent areas of
OL,13,Fcloud. Winds dropping out and staying
OL,14,Fmild overnight, but more comfortable
OL,15,Fthan recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
