OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA fine start to the weekend
OL,6,Fwith prolonged periods of sunshine.
OL,7,FCloud building a little more in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with an isolated shower
OL,9,Fpossible, but many staying dry. Less
OL,10,Fhot.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStaying
OL,13,Fdry into the second half of the
OL,14,Fweekend, with sunny spells by day and
OL,15,Fclear skies at night. Temperatures
OL,16,Ftrending a little nearer to average,
OL,17,Fbut still feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
